to install pmodel follow these instructions

1) go to the directory where you want to install the toolbox and unpack
	tar -xvf pModel-0.5.0.tar.gz

2) this generates a new <installdirectory>

3) link the launch script "bin/pmodel" from a PATH-directory. for example
	cd ~/bin
	ln -s <installdirectory>/bin/pmodel

checkout www.prozesskraft.de for more informations or tools.
